Let's all do our part to keep this a constructive space for everyone.

@linear-out I understand you're upset, but let's keep the discussion focused on the original topic and avoid personal remarks. We're here to learn from each other, so if you'd like to share your perspective or supporting evidence, I'm happy to engage. 

